PEEK paper authors
==================

The authors of the PEEK paper ("PEEK: Predictive Queue-Informed KV Cache
Management for LLM Serving") are listed below. Code in this repository was
written by Bing Xie; co-authors contributed to the research described in the
paper.

  Bing Xie       (corresponding author)
  Zhipeng Wang
  Masahiro Tanaka
  Zheng Zhen

See `paper/peek.pdf` for the full paper and `NOTICE` for the code copyright
notice.
